Don’t. Buy. Likes. ➡️➡️➡️ Get. Them. For. Free.
⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀
[Comment 🤑 if you NEED this]
⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀
Want to know how you can make your posts more ‘likeable’? 
⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀
💯 Post quality content: level up with HIGH RES photos. Have you scrolled through your feed and seen a boring, poor quality photo so just kept scrolling? Your audience is the same. Make sure you share the highest quality content that you can! Pro tip: white space is your friend.
⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀
💯Use targeted hashtags: there is no point in hashtagging ‘gymlife’ if your post is the best burger you have ever eaten and you want that company to see you! Use hashtags like #burgerislife or #burgeraddict - your posts will pop up in relevant places and people who are actually interested in food will see your HQ image and double tap for the love!!! 
⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀
💯 Double the amount of time spent on your caption: put some love into it! There's nothing worse than seeing a great image and and wanting the deets... but seeing no caption or just the hashtags in the caption. Spend some time writing what the post is about and including your hashtags at the end.
⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀
💯 Include your location: Locals love searching for locals! You've searched where you live on Instagram before, right? Geotag your location and allow other locals to see your content and resonate with it (they are either from where you are or have visited the place you’ve tagged!).
⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀
💯 Engage with other users: Don’t just sit back and hope that users will find your content - get engaged! Showing up in notifications is a GREAT prompt for users to click on your profile. Search relevant hashtags and engage with the most recent posts (recent = active).
⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀
@womanceomindset

node.text:
Here are 5 ways you can help yourself get from where you are to where you want to be: [swipe 👈🏼 then continue reading]
⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀
👉🏼Make sure you save this for those days you’re not feeling it.
⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀
1. Don’t let yesterday’s mistakes make you afraid of tomorrow.
⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀
Everyone has setbacks, challenges, failures, mistakes and adversities, but you always have a choice of what you carry ahead with you.
⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀
2. Treat every experience as a learning opportunity. 
⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀
There are no failures in life just lessons learned. 
⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀
4. Upgrade your circle. 
⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀
Surround yourself with people you can work with to create a powerful network of like- minded people who can help one another go to the next level.
⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀
Join our circle ⭕️ text “ Ceo Circle” to +1773-923-1411
⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀
5. Think bigger than yourself. 
⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀
Now and then we all find ourselves at a turning point, a time when life seems to be asking us to choose between staying stuck in the same place and moving out to something new where the destination is yet to be determined. 
⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀
If you venture out, the tests and hardships you meet along the way will boost your courage and help you become more than we ever thought possible.
⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀
Reinvent yourself as needed. 
⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀
Reinvention doesn't mean altering who you are or it may be as simple as a new method of pursuing the same dream.
⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀
Find a way ……. 
⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀
⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀
XO, 
⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀
@womanceomindset

Here are the ULTIMATE 5 steps I used to get 790K followers✨
⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀
Dm me ‘IGebook’ if you need my strategies! 🚀🙋🏻‍♀️
⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀
Being successful on social media is a BIG topic
⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀
More than the IG post character limit would allow!
⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀
So I’ve narrowed it down to:
⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀
👉 Know your audience. Your customers are what’s important so get clear on who your ideal client is and target them.
⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀
👉 Identify your goals. What’s your goal for using social media? Is it increasing revenue? Growing your leads? Directing people to your website?
⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀
👉 Have the right mindset. Be intentional in what you post. Make sure you’re giving value to your followers.
⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀
👉 Post the right content. Get clear on what you’re posting - does it entertain, educate, inspire? - and focus on the customer.
⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀
👉 ENGAGE! The biggest element of social media is being social. Make sure you’re interacting with your followers. Ask them a question and get them to engage with you.
⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀
It's time for you to STOP struggling on Instagram and learn current and proven hashtag strategies that I use in my own business to grow my followers. 📈💃🏻
